title: War of the Roses: The Dishes on the Floor
description: Carrie Ann's boyfriend, Ben, has a dog with his ex and she thinks that they are still hooking up because his ex is constantly calling with "issues" with the dog.  Before doing War of the Roses, Carrie Ann did something that everyone is calling crazy to try to catch Ben but didn't succeed so now she's on War of the Roses to try again!
